  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is a single-center, randomized, un-blinded treatment study in which patients (&gt;78
      years) with the use off a heart-lung machine were provided into two study arms.

      Patient wit &quot;precoating&quot; have a filling of the machine with their own blood. In the
      comparator arm, a standard priming is used.
    </textblock>
